article_title: Woman's body found in Hudson near Port Imperial
article_text:
A woman's body was found floating in the Hudson River near Port Imperial in West New York yesterday morning, officials said.

At around 7 a.m., a jogger noticed the body of the woman, believed to be about 30, authorities said.
